<title>INDIA: India 30-bln-rupee, 6-yr securities sale July 16.</title>
<headline>India 30-bln-rupee, 6-yr securities sale July 16.</headline>
<dateline>NEW DELHI 1997-07-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>The Indian government on Thursday announced the sale of six-year dated securities worth 30 billion rupees through an auction by the Reserve Bank of India (RBI) on July 16, a government statement said.  </p>
<p>&quot;The government stock is eligible for ready forward facility,&quot; the statement said.</p>
